  <brief_title>The Effects of Prolonged Standing Compared to Prolonged Sitting on Postprandial Lipemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Prolonged Standing Compared to Prolonged Sitting on Postprandial Lipemia</official_title>
