  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The effects of 12 hours of prolonged standing will be compared to prolonged standing on a
      high fat tolerance test the following day. Plasma triglycerides, insulin, and glucose will
      be measured in a crossover study design.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
